official_title: Medicare Annual Wellness Visit Practice Redesign Toolkit: A Tailored Intervention to Improve Preventive Health Services Use (Phase 2)
inclusion_criteria:
* have Medicare coverage
* aged 50 or older
* has at least one visit to the practice in the past 12 months
* not deceased

Practice eligibility criteria:

* care for patients with Medicare insurance
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 50 Years
miscellaneous_criteria: There are no inclusion or exclusion criteria based on sex/gender, race, and/or ethnicity.
